race.description: Our People, Our Pride At Wests Illawarra C1 Hcp
race.comment: OUI FLOURISH (12) won here on debut then went to Warwick Farm last start and produced a real eye-catcher, chiming in late to get up for second over today's distance. Progressive filly who makes plenty of appeal back in this company with a senior rider aboard. IN AND OUT (3) made a late dive but just missed when second-up over 1250m at the Kensington track last time out. Scored a big win third-up over 1300m at this circuit last prep. Should be hitting his peak for this. SAVVY SPY (8) has not appeared since winning on debut over 1500m at this track in October. Not asked for a lot in a couple of recent trials. Keep a close watch on the betting. SUN WARRIOR (9) displayed a nice turn of foot to record a soft win on debut over 1300m at Newcastle recently. Draws the fence and with some natural improvement can play a big role in this tougher race.
